Package tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.Obstacle

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    ObstacleSubscriber
    ObstacleSubscriber is an interface to apply Observer Design Pattern.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ExplosiveObstacle
    ExplosiveObstacle is a class that extends Obstacle which contains the attributes of an explosive obstacle.
    FirmObstacle
    FirmObstacle is a class that extends Obstacle which contains the attributes of a firm obstacle.
    FirstObstacleSubscriber
    Subscriber design pattern implementation to verify the detection of obstacle events to the developers.
    GiftObstacle
    GiftObstacle is a class that extends Obstacle which contains the attributes of a gift obstacle.
    HollowPurpleObstacle
    HollowPurpleObstacle is a class that one of the obstacle type which will be generated by the Ymir.
    Obstacle
    Obstacle is a class that extends ObstacleDescription which contains information regarding an obstacle's attributes.
    ObstacleFactory
    ObstacleFactory implements the Factory design pattern for the creation of similar but unique types of obstacles.
    ObstacleFactoryTest
    Test for ObstacleFactory
    ObstacleTest
    This class tests how the damageObstacle() method of Obstacle interacts with specific obstacles in specific situations.
    SimpleObstacle
    SimpleObstacle is a class that extends Obstacle which contains the attributes of a simple obstacle.
